  <AbilityBonus InternalName="ElvishEmpathy">
    <AbilityBonusOption InternalName="ElvishEmpathy">
      <!-- note this trait is coded into the elvish sovereign unittypes. The actual trait is just so there's a tooltip in-game.-->
      <DisplayName>Empathy</DisplayName>
      <Description>Elves prize the ability to be one with nature above all else. It is therefore tradition that the elf who is deemed to be the most empathic of the throne contenders is elected to rule.

Elvish sovereigns do not cause battle experience to be split as a result of being in the same army as another champion.</Description>
      <Icon>Ability_ArcaneVeil_Icon.png</Icon>
      <GameModifier>
        <Provides>Elves prize the ability to be one with nature above all else. It is therefore tradition that the elf who is deemed to be the most empathic of the throne contenders is elected to rule.

Elvish sovereigns do not cause battle experience to be split as a result of being in the same army as another champion.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <RarityDisplay>Rare</RarityDisplay>
      <AIData AIPersonality="AI_General">
        <AIPriority>5</AIPriority>
      </AIData>
    </AbilityBonusOption>
  </AbilityBonus>
  <AbilityBonus InternalName="MasterScoutAbility_Elves">
